ANTENNULE (
Fig. 18A–B
). 11-segmented, haplocer. All segments smooth, except for proximal and subdistal spinular rows on first segment. All setae smooth except for two and four biarticulated setae on tenth and eleventh segments, respectively. Armature formula: 1(1); 2(11); 3(6); 4(1); 5(5+(1+ ae)); 6(2); 7(2 +2 spines); 8(0); 9(1); 10(4); 11(5+ acro). Acrothek consisting of two setae and one aesthetasc fused basally.

